<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">I am not that knowledgeable about playing an Enchanter, but when my main, a 61 BL was grinding thru the 50's I did a lot of North Ro LDoN's and found having an Enchanter in those dungeons invaluable. 
<br />

<br />
In the late 50's, as your average level gets up, the mobs begin to gate, and run for friends. They are also hard to pacify, and tend to aggro through walls and doors. Having a chanter was a big help. 
<br />

<br />
Maybe setting up LFG in North Ro will get good results for groups.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
