<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">I would suggest staying in pon until you get COD (64). Why? There is a couple of things you can work on in pon. Reverse charming which you will use in Nobles Causeway(OOW). Learing how to mem blurr mob for full xp. Hoping it the full regen thingy won't kick in, but if so run to zone. Or mezz depending on level of comfort. But it will help you with hard hitting mobs and bringing them under control.
<br />

<br />
Travel in PON kill trees spiders birds and then move down and kill the gargoyles the big spiders near the gargoyles. 
<br />

<br />
And when you can kill all those mobs you will probably be close to 64. And off to HOH you go. 
