<span class="postbody">Once you have beckon you can charm a pestilance pulsling in pod this is the best pet you will find for the level restriction on your charm. The big spiders are fun but just to mr so wastes to much mana I would make one a pet sometimes just to get me healed up though when I needed it. Carefull pulling him though use your pacify, and try to keep him alive through blur as its a lot of mana to pacify and pull a new pet. One other thing there casters so they will fear your target mob once in a while or even snare it if your lucky but normally fear seems to be there favorite spell to cast and a runner in pod is we'll bad to say the least made for some amazing fights sometimes though. This guy hits around 355 max so buffed with mage gear he pretty wicked. Should be able to clear fouls, pestilance ,and corrupted buildings about three of them easy with this pet are Courtyards in pod with him. Trust me a lvl 57 pestilance pulsling is the pet you want.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
